weet]]'', ''[[Gaslight (1944 film)|Gaslight]]''; [[1st Golden Globe Awards]]\n* '''[[1945 in film|1945]]''' \u2013 ''[[Brief Encounter]]'', ''[[Leave Her to Heaven]]'', ''[[The Lost Weekend (film)|The Lost Weekend]]'', ''[[The Naughty Nineties]]'', ''[[Anchors Aweigh (film)|Anchors Aweigh]]'', ''[[The Picture of Dorian Gray (1945 film)|The Picture of Dorian Gray]]'', ''[[Rome, Open City]]'', ''[[Spellbound (1945 film)|Spellbound]]''\n* '''[[1946 in film|1946]]''' \u2013 ''[[It's a Wonderful Life]]'', ''[[Notorious (1946 film)|Notorious]]'', ''[[My Darling Clementine]]'', ''[[Great Expectations (1946 film)|Great Expectations]]'', ''[[The Best Years of Our Lives]]'', ''[[The Big Sleep (1946 film)|The Big Sleep]]'', ''[[Blue Skies (1946 film)|Blue Skies]]''; [[1946 Cannes Film Festival|First Cannes Film Festival]]\n* '''[[1947 in film|1947]]''' \u2013 ''[[Miracle on 34th Street (1947 film)|Miracle on 34th Street]]'', ''[[The Lady from Shanghai]]'', ''[[Monsieur Verdoux]]'', ''[[Out of the Past]]'', ''[[Odd Man Out]]''\n* '''[[1948 in film|1948]]''' \u2013 ''[[Bicycle Thieves]]'', ''[[The Red Shoes (1948 film)|The Red Shoes]]'', ''[[Red River (1948 film)|Red River]]'', ''[[Hamlet (1948 film)|Hamlet]]'', ''[[Easter Parade (film)|Easter Parade]]'', ''[[The Paleface (1948 film)|The Paleface]]'', ''[[The Treasure of the Sierra Madre (film)|The Treasure of the Sierra Madre]]''; [[1st British Academy Film Awards]]\n* '''[[1949 in film|1949]]''' \u2013 ''[[The Third Man]]'', ''[[All the King's Men (1949 film)|All the King's Men]]'', ''[[White Heat]]'', ''[[Whisky Galore! (1949 film)|Whisky Galore!]]'', ''[[Stray Dog (film)|Stray Dog]]s'', ''[[The Heiress]]'', ''[[On the Town (film)|On the Town]]''\n\n==1950s==\n{{See also|1950s in film}}\n* '''[[1950 in film|1950]]''' \u2013 ''[[Sunset Boulevard (film)|Sunset Boulevard]]'', ''[[All About Eve]]'', ''[[Cinderella (1950 film)|Cinderella]]'', ''[[Harvey (film)|Harvey]]'', ''[[Father of the Bride (1950 film)|Father of the Bride]]''