n| align=\"left\" | [[2010 NBA Playoffs|2010]]\n| align=\"left\" | [[2009\u201310 Boston Celtics season|Boston]]\n| 18 || 0 || 6.0 || .250 || .273 || '''1.000''' || .6 || .2 || .2 || .0 || .8\n|- class=\"sortbottom\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" colspan=\"2\"| Career\n| 129 || 96 || 30.3 || .418 || .388 || .866 || 3.5 || 1.8 || .8 || .2 || 11.8\n{{s-end}}\n\n====Finals====\n{{NBA player statistics start}}\n|- style=\"text-align: Center;\"\n|style=\"text-align:left;background:#afe6ba;\"| [[2007 NBA Finals|2007]]\u2020\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[2006\u201307 San Antonio Spurs season|San Antonio]]\n| '''4''' || '''4''' || '''18.5''' || '''.261''' || '''.083''' || '''.667''' || '''2.0''' || '''.8''' || '''1.3''' ||| '''.0''' || '''3.8'''\n|- style=\"text-align: Center;\"\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[2010 NBA Finals|2010]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| [[2009\u201310 Boston Celtics season|Boston]]\n| 2 || 0 || 2.5 || .000 || .000 || .000 || .0 || .0 || .0 ||| '''.0''' || .0\n|- class=\"sortbottom\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" colspan=\"2\"| Career\n| 6 || 4 || 13.2 || .250 || .077 || .667 || 1.3 || .5 || .7 || .0 || 2.5\n{{s-end}}\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of National Basketball Association career 3-point scoring leaders]]\n*[[List of National Basketball Association career playoff 3-point scoring leaders]]\n*[[List of National Basketball Association single-game steals leaders]]\n*[[List of National Basketball Association annual minutes leaders]]\n*[[List of National Basketball Association career minutes played leaders]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Michael Finley}}\n*{{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101201114938/http://www.nba.com/playerfile/michael_finley/ |date=December 1, 2010 |title=Michael Finley }} at NBA.com\n*{{basketball-reference}}\n*[http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/basketball/nba/players/3023/ SI.com \u2013 Pro Basketball \u2013 Michael Finley Player Page]\n*{{IMDb name|1186828}}\n\n{